title: Grateful Dead Live at Berkeley Community Theater on 1986-04-21
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step-> El Paso, Row Jimmy, My Brother Esau, Cumberland Blues, Desolation Row, Ramble On Rose, Let It Grow

Set 2

Touch Of Grey-> Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World*-> Drums*-> Maybe You Know**-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Morning Dew-> Around & Around-> Not Fade Away, E: Don't Ease Me In*

Rex Benefit *W/ Jose Lorenzo, **without Jerry & Phil Brent Played throught drums
